                (_≃ᴱ_.from (P≃Q x) y)))                                  ≡⟨ cong (λ eq → subst Q (_≃ᴱ_.left-inverse-of B≃A x) (_≃ᴱ_.to (P≃Q _) eq))
                                                                            substᴱ≡subst ⟩
        subst Q (_≃ᴱ_.left-inverse-of B≃A x)
